PassHasher is a simple Ruby on Rails app that I am creating to generate passwords similar to passwordmaker.org. Source Code is hosted on Github at PassHasher.

Goals:
Learn Rails 3
Do some design work
Brush up on Javascript
Maybe make something simpler and quicker to use than passwordmaker


http://bowerstudios.com/node/687



Deploy with Capistrano

Required Configuration:
Setup the database connection after you deploy by editing database.yml in shared/config

Setup the authentication mechanisms.  Uses omniauth, edit omniauth.yml in shared/config.  
Also update app/views/shared/_security_block.html.erb to reflect any additional (or less) options you choose for authentication.
